QuestData.Title: Holed Up
QuestData.Description: Oh, thank you! There's no way I could have made it back on my own.$B$BCome to think of it, there must be others around Firebough Nook that need to be rescued. Shall we go collect them and then head to the safety of Shado-Pan Fallback?
QuestData.LogDescription: Rescue Jin Warmkeg, Ya Firebough, Old Lady Fung, and Sya Zhong.
